  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study involves two tasks. The first involves observation of patient care during
      simulated aeroevacuation missions in order to gauge task saturation. The second involves
      review of records from actual evacuation flights in order to determine the effects of task
      saturation on patient care.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
